	   <div align="left" class="storytitle"> Book of Knowledge: Guide to Runnyeye</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Submitted by Akak </div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Dec 12, 2000, 17:19</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=%20Book%20of%20Knowledge%3A%20Guide%20to%20Runnyeye&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fguides%2FEverquest%2Farticle_47.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
